lead_paragraph: A 19-year-old striker from Qatar who was signed by Spanish club Villareal on Sunday is set to become the first player from his country to play in the Primera Liga and potentially the European Champions League.

headline.print_headline: Teenager Afif Set to Become First Qatari in La Liga
headline.main: Teenager Afif Set to Become First Qatari in La Liga
